trans-unit.source: Associates a well-known object type that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator with a remote endpoint that can process messages that are sent to a method on the type.
trans-unit.target: WSDL(Web Services Description Language) 생성기에 전달되는 잘 알려진 개체 형식을 형식에 있는 메서드로 보내진 메시지를 처리할 수 있는 원격 끝점에 연결합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType> class is used to hold information that is specified on the command line to the [Soapsuds Tool (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5) through the `-types` argument.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType> 클래스는 명령줄에 지정 된 정보를 저장 하는 데 사용 된 [Soapsuds 도구 (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5) 를 통해는 `-types` 인수.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType" /> class.
The object <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that is passed to the WSDL generator.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType" /> class with the object <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: WSDL(Web Services Description Language) 생성기로 전달되는 개체 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType" />을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The object <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that is passed to the WSDL generator.
The well-known endpoint that can process messages that are sent to a method on the object type that is specified in the <c>type</c> parameter.
trans-unit.target: <c>type</c> 매개 변수에 지정된 개체 형식의 메서드로 보내진 메시지를 처리하는 잘 알려진 끝점입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType" /> class with the URL and <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of an object that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: URL과 WSDL(Web Services Description Language) 생성자로 전달되는 개체의 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType" />을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: WSDL(Web Services Description Language) 생성기로 전달되는 개체 <see cref="T:System.Type" />을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The object <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that the current <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType" /> was created for.
Gets the URL of an object <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: WSDL(Web Services Description Language) 생성기로 전달되는 개체 <see cref="T:System.Type" />의 URL입니다.

trans-unit.source: The URL of an object <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that the current <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType" /> was created for.
